<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1023</hymn_number>
<title>jiǎ rú wǒ yǒu 迦南1023</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jiǎ rú wǒ yǒu qiān bàng yīng jīn zhōng guó kě yǐ quán shù zhī qǔ,
 jiǎ rú wǒ yǒu qiān tiáo shēng mìng, jué bù liú xià yī tiáo bù gěi zhōng guó.
 zhè shì shén de zhōng pū dài dé shēng de fèi fǔ zhī yán.
 gǎn dòng zhe lì dài de shèng tú, tà shàng le zhōng guó tǔ.
 fù a zhōng guó rén gǎn xiè nǐ, wǒ men xiàng nǐ fǔ fú.
 chà pài nǐ de hǎo pū rén, bǎ ài dài gěi zhōng huá mín zú.
 zhè kuài liáo kuò pín qióng yú mèi hēi àn de tǔ de, cóng cǐ méng le dà fú.
 dǎ kāi le shù qiān nián dǎ bù kāi de jié, jìn rù le guāng míng de guó dù.
 fù a wǒ men gǎn xiè nǐ, yě gǎn xiè nǐ de zhōng pū.
 sǎ rè xuè pāo tóu lú lì jīng jiān xīn, lì jīng xiū rǔ.
 zhǔ qiú nǐ ān wèi nǐ de pū rén, tā men méi yǒu kōng pǎo.
 jīn tiān zhōng guó zhèng yǒu wú shù de chuán dào rén, tà shàng zhè tiáo lù.</lyrics>
</song>